{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/heartbeat-season-4-segera-tayang-apakah-sam-dan-aiden-tetap-bersatu/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Heartbeat Season 4 Segera Tayang, Apakah Sam dan Aiden Tetap Bersatu?","content":"\n<p>Setelah mengakhiri kisahnya dengan berbagai teka-teki di akhir tahun lalu, bulan ini <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/heartbeat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Heartbeat  (opens in a new tab)\">Heartbeat </a>kembali tayang. Di <em>Seaso</em>n 4 ini, Heartbeat akan mengungkapkan jawaban dari pertanyaan-pertanyaan yang tersisa di <em>season</em> sebelumnya. Kira-kira akan seperti apa, ya? </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Berbagai Teka-Teki di Season Sebelumnya yang Akan Terjawab Kali Ini</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Heartbeat Season 4, Aiden dan Sam Akan Kembali Jadian?</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53546\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/heartbeat-season-4-segera-tayang-apakah-sam-dan-aiden-tetap-bersatu/attachment/heartbeat-season-4_meet/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_meet.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Heartbeat Season 4_meet\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_meet-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_meet.png\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_meet.png\" alt=\"Heartbeat Season 4_meet\" class=\"wp-image-53546\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_meet.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_meet-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Masih inget kan kalau di episode-episode menuju akhir <em>season </em>sebelumnya Aiden dan Sam sempat bertengkar. Apalagi Aiden kayaknya pengen banget melindungi ibunya. Mau gak mau kita harus melihat Aiden dan Sam berpisah. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Walaupun Aiden dan Sam sudah bertemu kembali, tapi apa iya mereka udah baikan? Apakah kira-kira kali ini mereka akan kembali bersatu seperti sebelum-sebelumnya? Atau mungkin ada tokoh baru yang akan menghiasi kisah cinta mereka?  Hmm, kita tunggu saja, ya. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ibunya Aiden Sembuh?</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53545\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/heartbeat-season-4-segera-tayang-apakah-sam-dan-aiden-tetap-bersatu/attachment/heartbeat-season-4_ibuaiden/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_ibuaiden.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Heartbeat Season 4_ibuaiden\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_ibuaiden-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_ibuaiden.png\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_ibuaiden.png\" alt=\"Heartbeat Season 4_ibuaiden\" class=\"wp-image-53545\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_ibuaiden.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_ibuaiden-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Buat yang selalu ngikutin <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/heartbeat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Heartbeat (opens in a new tab)\">Heartbeat</a>, pasti tau dong kalau Ibu dari Aiden mempunyai masalah gangguan kejiwaan. Nah, hal ini semakin diperparah karena Aiden tidak pernah membawa ibunya berobat. Bagi Aiden, selama ibunya dijauhkan dari hal-hal yang dapat menyebabkanny sakit, selama itu pula ibunya pasti akan baik-baik saja. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Namun akhirnya Ibunya Aiden harus dibawa ke rumah sakit karena keadaan yang semakin parah. Dengan dibawanya ibu Aiden ke rumah sakit, apakah akan membuat ibunya kembali seperti sedia kala?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pertarungan Aiden dan Sam di The Voiz 9. Berhasilkah mereka membawa hadiah untuk ibu Aiden?</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53547\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/heartbeat-season-4-segera-tayang-apakah-sam-dan-aiden-tetap-bersatu/attachment/heartbeat-season-4_thevoiz9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_thevoiz9.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Heartbeat Season 4_thevoiz9\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_thevoiz9-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_thevoiz9.png\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_thevoiz9.png\" alt=\"Heartbeat Season 4_thevoiz9\" class=\"wp-image-53547\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_thevoiz9.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_thevoiz9-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Seperti yang kita tau, di akhir cerita akhirnya Aiden memutuskan untuk mengikuti audisi menyanyi &#8220;The Voiz 9&#8221;. Hal ini pula yang membuat dia kembali berhubungan dengan Sam. (Balik ngomong loh, ya. Bukan balikan lagi). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu motivasi terbesar Aiden mengikuti ajang tersebut adalah demi membiayai pengobatan ibunya yang tidak murah itu. Kira-kira seperti apa lika-liku perlombaannya? Apakah mereka berhasil membawa hadiah guna membiayai penyembuhan ibu Aiden? </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ayah Aiden Muncul di <em>Season</em> 4</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53542\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/heartbeat-season-4-segera-tayang-apakah-sam-dan-aiden-tetap-bersatu/attachment/heartbeat-season-4_ayahaiden/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_AyahAiden.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Heartbeat Season 4_AyahAiden\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_AyahAiden-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_AyahAiden.png\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_AyahAiden.png\" alt=\"Heartbeat Season 4_AyahAiden\" class=\"wp-image-53542\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_AyahAiden.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_AyahAiden-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di akhir cerita pula, akhirnya kita diberitahu motivasi lain Aiden bersikeras untuk mengikuti lomba tersebut walaupun resikonya sangat tinggi. Gimana enggak, dia sampai harus meminta bantuan para dokter dan perawat di rumah sakit untuk mencegah ibunya melihat penampilannya dan juga menyuap sepupunya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53544\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/heartbeat-season-4-segera-tayang-apakah-sam-dan-aiden-tetap-bersatu/attachment/heartbeat-season-4_chat-violet/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_chat-violet.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Heartbeat Season 4_chat violet\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Nah, kira-kira kemana WIlliam? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_chat-violet-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_chat-violet.png\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_chat-violet.png\" alt=\"Heartbeat Season 4_chat violet\" class=\"wp-image-53544\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_chat-violet.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Heartbeat-Season-4_chat-violet-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Nah, kira-kira kemana WIlliam? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Hal ini karena dia mengetahui bahwa salah satu juri yang akan menilainya di ajang tersebut adalah ayah kandungnya sendiri!!!! Gila, kan. Seperti apa ya nanti saat mereka bertemu? Hmm, bikin makin penasaran.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Daripada menduga-duga, mending langsung aja baca keseruannya. Soalnya <strong>BESOK</strong>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Heartbeat  (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/heartbeat\" target=\"_blank\">Heartbeat </a><em>Season</em> 4 bakal tayang!!! Iya, tanggal <strong>9 April jam 8 Malam.&nbsp;</strong>Makanya jangan lupa pantengin <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics (opens in a new tab)\">CIAYO Comics</a> buat dapat <em>update </em>paling kekinian. </p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"006e1a4d-e11f-5208-b5f1-a4529547328c"}}}